'''Natus Vincere''' is an Ukrainian multigaming eSports organization formed in December 2009. They currently sponsor players and teams for 9 different games including VALORANT, Counter-Strike and Apex Legends. This page details the organization's CIS roster; for their European history, please see [[Natus Vincere]].

